<h1 style="color:#f8e8c7; font-size:2rem; margin-bottom:0.5rem; text-align:center;">
  Sir Keel Folke — The Lion Set Aside
</h1>

<p style="text-align:center; opacity:0.85; margin-bottom:1.5rem;">
  Veteran knight • Fortress Commander of Broederports • A hero placed beyond the battlefield
</p>

<div style="
  background:#131316;
  padding:1.25rem 1.5rem;
